high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the dishwasher.
Pick up the cup from the coffee machine.
Turn to your left and look at the microwave.
Heat the cup up in the microwave.
Turn to your right and look at the coffee machine.
Place the cup under the spout of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved cup under the spout of the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the coffee maker.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and heat it.
Turn right to face the coffee maker.
Put the mug back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the microwave on the left.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the heated mug to the coffee machine on the right.
Put the heated mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.
